[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m For other primes: 
[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m - 89: appears in 89 Г— 178 in 200! but not in 100! Г— 100!
[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m - 83: appears in 83 Г— 166 in 200! but not in 100! Г— 100!
[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=19626)[0m But 97 > 89, 83, so the largest 2-digit prime factor is 97.
